thub.com/users/thegasta/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2025-04-05T13:58:20Z","updated_at":"2025-04-05T13:58:20Z","body":"Same problem in my debian 12 server.\nSyncthing version seems to be indifferent, I'm still facing this issue on `1.29.4`.\nI'm using the default systemd unit file shipped with syncthing.\n\nDefault folder settings:\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8346ea35-1e8c-4da0-8c22-6a571fea06c9)\n\nFrom now on, all actions/commands are done with `syncthing` user.\nSyncthing data folder permissions and ACL (let's call it `datadir`):\n(reminder: with `getfacl -t` capital letter means 'not effective')\n```\ndrwxrwx---+ 56 root      root       56 Apr  5 12:32 .\n\n> getfacl -t .\n# file: .\nUSER   root       rwx  rwx\nuser   syncthing  rwx  rwx\nGROUP  root       r-x  r-x\ngroup  syncthing  r-x  r-x\nmask              rwx  rwx\nother             ---  ---\n```\n\nWhen creating a dir from the console (`datadir/test-from-console`) or from the GUI (`datadir/test-from-gui`) everything works, in particular you can see that mask is kept as `rwx`.\nWhen creating the folder from another Syncthing device (`datadir/test-from-other-device`, shared by default with the server), the mask is set to `---`.\nSame happens with (`datadir/test-from-other-device-no-ignore-perm`, shared by default with the server), to do this test I disabled `Ignore permissions` in default folder settings.\n```\ndrwxrwx---+  2 syncthing syncthing   2 Apr  5 13:55 test-from-console\ndrwxrwx---+  3 syncthing syncthing   3 Apr  5 13:05 test-from-gui\ndrwx------+  3 syncthing syncthing   4 Apr  5 13:10 test-from-other-device\n\nroot@pve1:/pve1-raidz/pve1-data1# getfacl -t test-from-*\n# file: test-from-console\nUSER   syncthing  rwx  rwx\nuser   syncthing  rwx  rwx\nGROUP  syncthing  r-x  r-x\ngroup  syncthing  r-x  r-x\nmask              rwx  rwx\nother             ---  ---\n\n# file: test-from-gui1\nUSER   syncthing  rwx  rwx\nuser   syncthing  rwx  rwx\nGROUP  syncthing  r-x  r-x\ngroup  syncthing  r-x  r-x\nmask              rwx  rwx\nother             ---  ---\n\n# file: test-from-other-device\nUSER   syncthing  rwx  rwx\nuser   syncthing  RWX  rwx                  << capital letter means 'not effective'\nGROUP  syncthing  R-X  r-x\ngroup  syncthing  R-X  r-x\nmask              ---  rwx                  << notice the mask not following default\nother             ---  ---\n\n# file: from-other-device-no-ignore-perm\nUSER   syncthing  rwx  rwx\nuser   syncthing  RWX  rwx\nGROUP  syncthing  R-X  r-x\ngroup  syncthing  R-X  r-x\nmask              ---  rwx\nother             ---  ---\n```\n\nIn the same way I tried with files, `from-*.txt` file names indicate from where they were created.\nBelow the details within the problematic folder:\n```\n> getfacl -tR test-from-other-device\n# dir omitted, just shown above\n\n# file: test-from-other-device/.stfolder\nUSER   syncthing  rwx  rwx\nuser   syncthing  rWx  rwx\nGROUP  syncthing  r-x  r-x\ngroup  syncthing  r-x  r-x\nmask              r-x  rwx\nother             ---  ---\n\n# file: test-from-other-device/.stfolder/syncthing-folder-181db0.txt\nUSER   syncthing  rw-     \nuser   syncthing  rWX     \nGROUP  syncthing  r-X     \ngroup  syncthing  r-X     \nmask              r--     \nother             ---     \n\n# file: test-from-other-device/.stignore\nUSER   syncthing  rw-     \nuser   syncthing  RWX     \nGROUP  syncthing  R-X     \ngroup  syncthing  R-X     \nmask              ---     \nother             ---     \n\n# file: test-from-other-device/from-console.txt\nUSER   syncthing  rw-     \nuser   syncthing  rwX     \nGROUP  syncthing  r-X     \ngroup  syncthing  r-X     \nmask              rw-     \nother             ---     \n\n# file: test-from-other-device/from-console-root.txt\nUSER   root       rw-     \nuser   syncthing  rwX     \nGROUP  root       r-X     \ngroup  syncthing  r-X     \nmask              rw-     \nother             ---     \n\n# file: test-from-other-device/from-other-device.txt\nUSER   syncthing  rw-     \nuser   syncthing  rwX     \nGROUP  syncthing  r-X     \ngroup  syncthing  r-X     \nmask              rw-     \nother             ---     \n```\n\n\nConclusion:\nthe problem seems to be related only to folders received (auto-accepted or not).","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/syncthing/syncthing/issues/comments/2780736803/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"thegasta","id":10324673,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwMzI0Njcz","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/10324673?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta","html_url":"https://github.com/thegasta","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/thegasta/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"id":1761480